OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777662668
OL,3,CWoman's body found on beach as police
OL,4,Cinvestigate 'unexplained' death
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a
OL,7,Fwoman's body was discovered on a
OL,8,FWearside beach.
OL,10,FNorthumbria Police have said they were
OL,11,Fcalled to Seaburn beach, just after
OL,12,F5am on Friday 1 May.
OL,14,FOfficers attended alongside other
OL,15,Femergency services, where the body of
OL,16,Fa woman was located.
OL,18,FA police presence remains in the area
OL,19,Fas enquiries continue to formally
OL,20,Fidentify the woman.
