OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1777662668
OL,3,CWoman's body found on beach as police
OL,4,Cinvestigate 'unexplained' death
OL,6,FA spokesperson from Northumbria Police
OL,7,Fhas said: "Just after 5am today
OL,8,F(Friday), we received a report that
OL,9,Fthe body had been found on Seaburn
OL,10,FBeach in Whitburn.
OL,12,F"Emergency services attended the scene
OL,13,Fwhere the body of a woman was sadly
OL,14,Flocated.
OL,16,F"A police presence is currently in the
OL,17,Farea and enquiries are underway to
OL,18,Fformally identify the person and
OL,19,Fnotify their next of kin.
